&lt;code&gt;
  validates_length_of :mobile,
                      :in =&gt; 10..20,
                      :on =&gt; :create,
                      :message =&gt; &quot;Sample: 5329999999&quot;
&lt;/code&gt;

using :minimum and :maximum instead of :in works fine anyway

This is on 2.1.1</original-body>
